author: Written by: FOX8Live.com Staff
title: All lanes reopened on I-12 near Livingston
text:
NEW ORLEANS (WVUE) - Interstate-12 headed eastbound was closed before Livingston due to an overturned vehicle.
Officers say it has reopened. Expect delays.
